  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "883e9c05-d069-46ad-afb0-43085b1d8c6b",
    "name": "cs2031-2025-2-week01-lab01",
    "description": "Colección de Postman para probar la API de gestión de usuarios con autenticación por API Key.\n\n**Instrucciones:**\n1. Importa esta colección en Postman\n2. Configura la variable `base_url` como http://localhost:3000\n3. Ejecuta el login para obtener tu API key\n4. Copia el API key y úsalo en el header `x-api-key` para otros requests\n\n**Autenticación:**\n- Usar header: `x-api-key: {API_KEY_AQUI}`\n- O header: `Authorization: Bearer {API_KEY_AQUI}`\n\n**Variable:**\n- base_url: URL de tu API (ej: http://localhost:3000)",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_exporter_id": "34026023",
    "_collection_link": "https://alejandroen-team.postman.co/workspace/dbp-2025-2~c8616997-14c2-415d-8397-755504e22f5e/collection/34026023-883e9c05-d069-46ad-afb0-43085b1d8c6b?action=share&source=collection_link&creator=34026023"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Authentication",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Register User",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"student_test\",\n  \"email\": \"daniel.sandoval.t@utec.edu.pe\",\n  \"password\": \"TestPass123\",\n  \"name\": \"Test Student\",\n  \"age\": 20,\n  \"description\": \"Test student for API testing\",\n  \"career\": \"Computer Science\",\n  \"hobbies\": \"Programming, Gaming\",\n  \"role\": \"student\",\n  \"section\": \"1.02\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/register",
              "host": [
                "{{base_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "auth",
                "register"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Registra un nuevo usuario. Solo emails que existen en la tabla `identifiers` pueden registrarse."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Register User - Invalid Email",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
